dc_description_s: This dataset contains 8 layers describing the geology of Blue Mounds State Park. The work used to produce this data was published in this report: GEOLOGY OF BLUE MOUNDS STATE PARK For documentation of the indivual layers, see the metadata files associated with those layers: Structure - Bedding Structure - Peleocurrent Directions Structure - Glacial Structures Geologic Stations Geologic Features Fractures Outcrop Bedrock Geologic Units
